summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to City Street Classifications; amending the Traffic Code Arterial Map, known as Exhibit 11.18.010A, referenced in Seattle Municipal Code 11.18.010 (part of the Traffic Code); and amending the Seattle Comprehensive Transportation Program (SCTP) Traffic Classifications Map, by removing 11th Avenue Southwest, between Southwest Florida Street and Southwest Spokane Street from the designated class of arterials and reclassifying 11th Avenue Southwest, from Southwest Florida Street to Southwest Lander Street as a Commercial Access Street.
